59
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,640
Princess.

60
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,998
Brother!

61
00:03:13,999 --> 00:03:14,718
Ms. Wu!

62
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,519
Ms. Wu!

63
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:16,839
I know.

64
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,759
Don't cremate him.

65
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,560
I know you can't believe it.

66
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,840
But your brother is seriously ill.

67
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:24,519
Don't chase him.

68
00:03:26,239 --> 00:03:29,279
But now he's not painful anymore.

69
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,400
Last night,

70
00:03:39,359 --> 00:03:41,279
I hummed a ditty

71
00:03:41,999 --> 00:03:43,480
to put him to sleep.

72
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:47,400
Suddenly, he had a high fever

73
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:50,480
and black spots on his skin.

74
00:03:51,279 --> 00:03:54,480
Then his body became cold.

75
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,920
Slowly.

76
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:05,039
I rubbed his hands, feet and face.

77
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,719
But he became totally cold.

78
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,079
I can do nothing.

79
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,839
He died.

80
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,640
Ms. Wu.

81
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:18,238
Your brother became bereaved after birth.

82
00:04:18,239 --> 00:04:21,519
It's already hard for you to raise him up.

83
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,959
It's lucky that you're sister and brother.

84
00:04:26,719 --> 00:04:27,719
