85
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:34,040
He's not had enough rice and steamed buns.

86
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:37,200
<i>He came to this world</i>

87
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:40,878
<i>but left as if he had never existed, why?</i>

88
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:43,759
<i>When we arrive in Luoyang, I can give you anything you want.</i>

89
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:48,240
<i>I want you to give me a lot of rice.</i>

90
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,959
<i>I've never tasted rice.</i>

91
00:04:55,800 --> 00:05:02,079
I know your brother went to see your parents in the nether world.

92
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,640
