135
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:14,159
I'll feel a bit relieved.

136
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,400
Go!

137
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,639
Stop!

138
00:08:33,839 --> 00:08:34,959
Any information of Changge?

139
00:08:35,959 --> 00:08:37,919
Mr. Qin. I have the news.

140
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,718
We found a person similar to Young Master.

141
00:08:39,719 --> 00:08:42,680
She went to Luoyang with a doctor and a young man in a donkey cart.

142
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,718
Who are the doctor and the man?

143
00:08:46,719 --> 00:08:48,079
Is Changge safe with them?

144
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:50,439
Stop pretending to care about her.

145
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,239
We'll find Commander Li.

146
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,239
None of your business!

147
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,040
Xu Feng.

148
00:08:55,319 --> 00:08:57,039
He's impetuous.

149
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,838
He never cares about what he says.

150
00:08:58,839 --> 00:09:01,078
But he's always loyal to Young Master.

151
00:09:01,079 --> 00:09:02,480
Don't think too much.

152
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:11,519
So we should speed up and arrive in Luoyang as soon as possible.

153
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:21,479
Since we're all for Young Master's good,

154
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,880
