155
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:26,439
During these days,

156
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:29,759
haven't you found that he really cares about Young Master?

157
00:09:35,199 --> 00:09:36,919
Even if he really cares about Young Master,

158
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:41,879
