00:15:26,619 --> 00:15:27,019
Painful.

281
00:15:27,020 --> 00:15:27,820
Still painful?

282
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:36,099
Thank you for saving me.

283
00:15:39,140 --> 00:15:40,299
Tell me your name.

284
00:15:41,179 --> 00:15:42,500
I'll give you money.

285
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:45,099
I'll repay you.

286
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:46,940
You're welcome.

287
00:15:48,659 --> 00:15:49,899
Mister!

288
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:50,700
Mister!

289
00:15:52,059 --> 00:15:52,859
Here you are.

290
00:15:55,299 --> 00:15:56,099
Back!

291
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:57,699
Back!

292
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:58,538
Mister, are you OK?

293
00:15:58,539 --> 00:15:59,298
Come back!

294
00:15:59,299 --> 00:16:00,099
Are you OK?

295
00:16:02,219 --> 00:16:03,260
Back!

296
00:16:19,739 --> 00:16:20,779
Give me a pie.

297
00:16:20,780 --> 00:16:21,580
Here you are.

298
00:16:24,539 --> 00:16:26,260
Brother A'Zhun.

299
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:30,979
Do you like this song?

300
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:36,180
Lazy bone!

301
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:56,419
Xu Feng is right.

302
00:16:57,219 --> 00:16:59,298
You shouldn't get too close to me.

303
00:16:59,299 --> 00:17:00,500
Why?

304
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:05,300
Yuan.

305
00:17:07,859 --> 00:17:09,339
It's a wolf whistle.

306
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:10,619
It's our specialty.

307
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:13,540
I have nothing else to compensate you.

308
00:17:14,819 --> 00:17:17,619
Blow it when in need.

309
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:21,859
I'll protect you on behalf of your parents.

310
00:17:25,219 --> 00:17:26,779
In this way?

311
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:27,580
Very good.

312
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:45,400
<i>[Sun]</i>

313
00:17:59,619 --> 00:18:00,739
What am I thinking about?

314
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:04,698
New trouble arose as soon as His Highness came here, why?

315
00:18:04,699 --> 00:18:05,739
His Highness?

316
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:16,699
I'll finish.

317
00:18:21,099 --> 00:18:21,899
More ointment.

318
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:23,060
Don't touch water.

319
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:26,860
Bear the pain.

320
00:18:28,339 --> 00:18:29,059
A' Bi!

321
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:30,458
What happened?

322
00:18:30,459 --> 00:18:32,738
His Highness secretly watched juggling and spread money

323
00:18:32,739 --> 00:18:35,938
on the street instead of comforting the refugees after he came to Luoyang.

324
00:18:35,939 --> 00:18:38,979
But the street was so crowded that many people were trampled on.

325
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:40,420
His Highness is here?

326
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:45,900
He never did anything right.

327
00:18:48,099 --> 00:18:48,899
My apprentice.

328
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,858
Let me bandage it for you.

329
00:18:52,859 --> 00:18:55,499
If you have spare time to care about the official affairs,

330
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:57,420
you'd better work with me in South Hill.

331
00:18:58,979 --> 00:18:59,779
Let's go!

332
00:19:09,219 --> 00:19:10,218
Your Highness.

333
00:19:10,219 --> 00:19:12,299
Mr. Wei, finally you come!

334
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:14,169
People outside seem to be mad.

335
00:19:14,170 --> 00:19:15,179
I want to return to Chang'an!

336
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,159
Get the carriage ready!

337
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:17,320
I want to return to Chang'an!

338
00:19:19,339 --> 00:19:20,339
You're injured.

339
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:22,420
How did you protect him?

340
00:19:24,020 --> 00:19:25,938
They're a bunch of thugs!

341
00:19:25,939 --> 00:19:27,539
I spread money to them out of kindness.

342
00:19:27,540 --> 00:19:29,139
But the outcome is terrible.

343
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:30,858
Some people were trampled to death.

344
00:19:30,859 --> 00:19:31,939
Too terrible!

345
00:19:32,459 --> 00:19:33,659
I want to go back to Chang'an!

346
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:35,420
What trouble did you make?

347
00:19:36,619 --> 00:19:37,818
Sister.

348
00:19:37,819 --> 00:19:39,019
I'm injured.

349
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:40,500
But why don't you care about me?

350
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:42,779
You show no kindness to me at all!

351
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:43,580
Let me see.

352
00:19:46,739 --> 00:19:47,539
Chengqian!

353
00:19:48,819 --> 00:19:49,618
Brother Shuyu.

354
00:19:49,619 --> 00:19:50,779
Look around with me.

355
00:19:50,780 --> 00:19:51,580
- Go.
- Princess.

356
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:54,099
It's my duty.

357
00:19:54,739 --> 00:19:57,660
Keep an eye on His Highness lest he wants to go back to Chang'an.

358
00:19:58,979 --> 00:20:00,979
Okay. Thank you.

359
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:10,700
Move out of my way!

360
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:14,698
- Commander!
- Go!

361
00:20:14,699 --> 00:20:15,659
Be lenient on me!

362
00:20:15,660 --> 00:20:16,349
Commander!

363
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,299
- Stand up!
- Commander!

364
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:18,499
Please be lenient on me!

365
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:19,660
Hurry up!

366
00:20:23,219 --> 00:20:23,899
Commander.

367
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:25,419
It's these beggars who made troubles.

368
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,899
Commander, please be lenient on me!

369
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,059
We're not on purpose.

370
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,499
We've been hungry for days.

371
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:30,978
A rich man spread money in the street.

372
00:20:30,979 --> 00:20:32,659
We just picked several more coppers.

373
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:34,338
We didn't expect things should go wrong.

374
00:20:34,339 --> 00:20:35,219
Commander.

375
00:20:41,939 --> 00:20:43,698
<i>I know very well the people outside.</i>

376
00:20:43,699 --> 00:20:45,219
<i>They're just too hungry.</i>

377
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:48,779
<i>Some people are kind on the surface, but vicious inside.</i>

378
00:20:48,780 --> 00:20:53,500
<i>Some people look indifferent but are warmhearted, like you.</i>

379
00:20:56,859 --> 00:20:59,698
Take them back and let Magistrate deal with them.

380
00:20:59,699 --> 00:21:00,858
Yes.

381
00:21:00,859 --> 00:21:01,659
Go!

382
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:02,499
Commander!

383
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:03,659
Be lenient on me!

384
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:05,698
Commander, show mercy on me!

385
00:21:05,699 --> 00:21:06,499
Hurry up!

386
00:21:28,339 --> 00:21:29,260
Slow down.

387
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:39,300
Slow down.

388
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:14,380
Are you feeling better?

389
00:22:15,219 --> 00:22:16,019
Bear the pain.

390
00:22:24,339 --> 00:22:26,060
Why are there so many refugees?

391
00:22:27,459 --> 00:22:29,540
They used to be ordinary people.

392
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:32,780
In the face of disaster and war, they became refugees.

393
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:38,140
As long as society is not stable, there will be more refugees.

394
00:22:39,020 --> 00:22:41,459
Feel uncomfortable at the sight of that?

395
00:22:42,140 --> 00:22:44,738
They are more fortunate than those who have no place to live

396
00:22:44,739 --> 00:22:45,780
and no food to eat.

397
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:49,259
Some of those who have not escaped the disaster and war

398
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:53,020
are still wandering and struggling,

399
00:22:53,660 --> 00:22:57,618
while some of them have been buried in the earth

400
00:22:57,619 --> 00:22:59,180
and have no chance to live.

401
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:02,140
My friend.

402
00:23:03,579 --> 00:23:04,900
Here you come.

403
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:10,060
Master.

404
00:23:11,020 --> 00:23:11,820
Master.

405
00:23:12,859 --> 00:23:13,660
Here you come.

406
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,060
Ms. Wu.

407
00:23:15,939 --> 00:23:18,738
Master, who's this sister?

408
00:23:18,739 --> 00:23:20,939
Is she new here to cultivate herself?

409
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:23,379
Ms. Wu.

410
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:25,698
She's A' Li.

411
00:23:25,699 --> 00:23:27,659
She's been cultivating herself in the temple.

412
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:29,499
I'm busy today.

413
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:33,219
Can you take her to go outside tomorrow?

414
00:23:42,780 --> 00:23:43,580
My apprentice.

415
00:23:44,180 --> 00:23:46,019
Aren't you called Li Changge?

416
00:23:46,020 --> 00:23:47,260
When did you change your name?

417
00:23:47,859 --> 00:23:51,060
What I'm called doesn't matter.

418
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:54,259
Okay.

419
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:56,619
Change your name and restart your life.

420
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:09,200
<i>[Luoyang]</i>

421
00:24:10,900 --> 00:24:11,739
Have you found her?

422
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:13,499
No.

423
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:15,299
I searched there but in vain.

424
00:24:15,300 --> 00:24:17,578
Search in all directions!

425
00:24:17,579 --> 00:24:18,379
Yes!

426
00:24:21,819 --> 00:24:22,978
What happened?

427
00:24:22,979 --> 00:24:24,300
Yuan is missing.

428
00:24:25,579 --> 00:24:26,539
Yuan is missing!

429
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:27,818
You're the only one out there.

430
00:24:27,819 --> 00:24:29,179
Didn't you see anyone running out?

431
00:24:33,020 --> 00:24:33,938
Stop!

432
00:24:33,939 --> 00:24:34,739
Xu Feng.

433
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:36,618
Listen.

434
00:24:36,619 --> 00:24:38,218
If there's anything wrong with Yuan,

435
00:24:38,219 --> 00:24:40,419
I'll get even with you for all the matters.

436
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:42,260
I'll kill you for Gongsun family.

437
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,500
First, find her.

438
00:24:45,099 --> 00:24:46,060
Then it's up to you.

439
00:24:55,819 --> 00:24:56,619
Where to go?

440
00:25:19,339 --> 00:25:20,139
Yuan!

441
00:25:25,300 --> 00:25:26,100
Yuan!

442
00:25:28,739 --> 00:25:29,539
Are you OK?

443
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:30,340
I'm fine.

444
00:25:31,260 --> 00:25:32,458
Let me take you out.

445
00:25:32,459 --> 00:25:33,259
OK?

446
00:25:35,819 --> 00:25:36,619
Come on.

447
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:46,618
Yuan.

448
00:25:46,619 --> 00:25:48,899
Why are you here?

449
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:51,698
Tomorrow is mom's birthday.

450
00:25:51,699 --> 00:25:55,338
I want to pick some flowers for her.

451
00:25:55,339 --> 00:25:59,539
I saw flowers on the tree, but I couldn't reach them.

452
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:02,260
I didn't expect to fall into the pit.

453
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:06,458
What a good girl!

454
00:26:06,459 --> 00:26:08,140
You are filial.

455
00:26:09,219 --> 00:26:14,859
Gongsun's greatest wish is that you can be safe and happy.

456
00:26:16,619 --> 00:26:19,639
It's a pity that he can help all people in his life

457
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:23,140
but can't protect his family.

458
00:26:25,859 --> 00:26:28,699
Well, let's go back.

459
00:26:33,979 --> 00:26:34,779
Nothing serious.

460
00:26:41,500 --> 00:26:43,540
You can't do this again.

461
00:26:45,020 --> 00:26:46,019
Painful?

462
00:26:46,020 --> 00:26:49,938
I will immediately count the number of injured and the registered residence of each household.

463
00:26:49,939 --> 00:26:53,660
Please come with me to comfort them and give them subsidies.

464
00:26:55,739 --> 00:26:58,020
Mr. Wei, you can do it alone.

465
00:26:58,619 --> 00:27:00,458
Or I wouldn't have brought you here.

466
00:27:00,459 --> 00:27:03,059
How can you talk to Brother Shuyu like that?

467
00:27:03,060 --> 00:27:05,139
It's all your fault.

468
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:06,779
You should comfort those people.

469
00:27:06,780 --> 00:27:07,539
Sister.

470
00:27:07,540 --> 00:27:08,698
My kindness is not rewarded.

471
00:27:08,699 --> 00:27:10,139
I gave them money but was hurt.

472
00:27:10,140 --> 00:27:11,019
I'm sad.

473
00:27:11,020 --> 00:27:12,458
Leave me alone!

474
00:27:12,459 --> 00:27:13,779
You're Crown Prince.

475
00:27:13,780 --> 00:27:16,219
If you don't go, should I go?

476
00:27:17,420 --> 00:27:19,659
So you said you would go.

477
00:27:19,660 --> 00:27:20,059
I...

478
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:20,938
You're Princess of Tang.

479
00:27:20,939 --> 00:27:22,019
You should do that.

480
00:27:22,020 --> 00:27:28,140
Last time you comforted those refugees in person.

481
00:27:29,699 --> 00:27:30,619
Sister.

482
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:32,179
I've already been injured.

483
00:27:32,180 --> 00:27:34,339
Let me have a rest for a few days.

484
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:41,779
Let me see how long you can be so willful.

485
00:27:41,780 --> 00:27:42,900
Sister.

486
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,300
Come on.

487
00:27:48,020 --> 00:27:51,098
I'll go on your behalf.

488
00:27:51,099 --> 00:27:52,180
But just this once.

489
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:00,700
Mr. Wei.

490
00:28:03,219 --> 00:28:04,299
Mr. Wei.

491
00:28:04,300 --> 00:28:05,859
I dare not go into the street again.

492
00:28:06,660 --> 00:28:09,339
Anywhere else can I go?

493
00:28:10,099 --> 00:28:12,218
I heard that Ziwei Palace of Sui Dynasty is here.

494
00:28:12,219 --> 00:28:14,179
Can you go with me?

495
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,139
Your Highness.

496
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:17,978
It was built by Emperor Yang. It's a sheer waste of energy and money.

497
00:28:17,979 --> 00:28:20,818
I think you'd better go to visit common people.

498
00:28:20,819 --> 00:28:22,419
Anyway, his Majesty appointed you...

499
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:24,019
Yes.

500
00:28:24,020 --> 00:28:25,379
I think you're right.

501
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:28,618
You should watch Luoyang carefully, especially Ziwei Palace.

502
00:28:28,619 --> 00:28:30,618
Emperor Yang was quite extravagant.

503
00:28:30,619 --> 00:28:34,179
I have to see the palace
in detail as a reminder.

504
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,939
Get the carriage ready!

505
00:28:41,979 --> 00:28:45,179
Wound healing unguent. Blood recovering pills.

506
00:28:45,180 --> 00:28:46,619
Medicine is ready.

507
00:28:48,619 --> 00:28:50,618
Princess, why not go with Mr. Hao?

508
00:28:50,619 --> 00:28:51,620
<i>[Anti-plague pills]</i>

509
00:28:54,020 --> 00:28:55,339
No need.

510
00:28:56,459 --> 00:28:57,979
It's not the case in Chang'an.

511
00:28:58,699 --> 00:29:00,338
There are many refugees.

512
00:29:00,339 --> 00:29:01,819
They came from many different places.

513
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:04,738
Mr. Wei will take care of his Highness.

514
00:29:04,739 --> 00:29:06,140
So he can't accompany you.

515
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:10,939
But I'm afraid if Mr. Hao isn't here, either.

516
00:29:11,780 --> 00:29:13,419
I'm either in the mansion or in South Hill.

517
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,819
He'll find me for sure.

518
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:16,500
By the way,

519
00:29:17,540 --> 00:29:19,578
it's impossible that he follows me all his life.

520
00:29:19,579 --> 00:29:21,180
We should be able to protect ourselves.

521
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:24,899
Princess, you really change a lot.

522
00:29:24,900 --> 00:29:26,818
It's better that Mr. Hao doesn't follow you.

523
00:29:26,819 --> 00:29:30,619
Sometimes I'm scared at the sight of him.

524
00:29:32,180 --> 00:29:33,578
Yes.

525
00:29:33,579 --> 00:29:36,380
I was also afraid of him before.

526
00:29:37,060 --> 00:29:38,218
Before?

527
00:29:38,219 --> 00:29:40,300
Now you're not afraid of him?

528
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:43,060
Now...

529
00:29:46,260 --> 00:29:47,060
<i>Princess!</i>

530
00:29:50,339 --> 00:29:51,380
<i>I finally find you!</i>

531
00:29:53,219 --> 00:29:55,260
<i>Let me take you home.</i>

532
00:30:00,739 --> 00:30:02,098
Yesterday, Master asked me

533
00:30:02,099 --> 00:30:04,380
to take you to South Hill today to look around.

534
00:30:09,020 --> 00:30:10,180
Sister A' Li.

535
00:30:10,699 --> 00:30:12,819
Do you have anything in mind?

536
00:30:13,780 --> 00:30:16,300
You looked blue yesterday.

537
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:19,578
Why do you live in the temple?

538
00:30:19,579 --> 00:30:20,660
Where's your family?

539
00:30:21,939 --> 00:30:23,380
They all died.

540
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:28,180
Sister A' Li.

541
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:30,098
Here you are.

542
00:30:30,099 --> 00:30:31,499
The candy was given from Master.

543
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:33,019
I haven't had it.

544
00:30:33,020 --> 00:30:33,939
Here you are.

545
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:36,819
You want to give it to me?

546
00:30:38,500 --> 00:30:39,978
Sister A' Li.

547
00:30:39,979 --> 00:30:41,020
Don't be sad.

548
00:30:41,979 --> 00:30:45,819
In fact, my family also died.

549
00:30:46,339 --> 00:30:49,059
The people I met yesterday are not your family?

550
00:30:49,060 --> 00:30:51,260
I used to live in Yunzhou.

551
00:30:51,819 --> 00:30:54,139
When winter is approaching,

552
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:56,540
people from the grassland will come to loot.

553
00:30:57,140 --> 00:30:59,619
Later, in the year of disaster,

554
00:31:00,180 --> 00:31:02,020
no one could survive.

555
00:31:02,739 --> 00:31:05,660
Our parents took us out.

556
00:31:06,459 --> 00:31:10,140
They said we could survive in the south.

557
00:31:12,979 --> 00:31:18,979
But later, my dad died of disease.

558
00:31:19,979 --> 00:31:22,739
Then my mom also fell ill.

559
00:31:23,540 --> 00:31:26,899
She said that ordinary people like us

560
00:31:26,900 --> 00:31:28,739
can only depend on heaven for food;

561
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:31,939
if God wants to take back your life,

562
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:34,699
you can only accept such fate.

563
00:31:36,780 --> 00:31:38,338
It shouldn't be the case.

564
00:31:38,339 --> 00:31:41,699
But I can do nothing.

565
00:31:42,339 --> 00:31:43,738
My parents died.

566
00:31:43,739 --> 00:31:46,219
I took my little brother all the way to Liuyun Taoist Temple.

567
00:31:47,699 --> 00:31:50,780
A few days ago, my brother died, too.

568
00:31:51,619 --> 00:31:53,459
I miss him very much.

569
00:31:54,020 --> 00:31:57,979
But I was told that people won't feel pain after death.

570
00:31:58,579 --> 00:32:01,140
So he won't suffer anymore.

571
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:04,059
Is that true?

572
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:05,300
Sister A' Li.

573
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:07,459
Yes.

574
00:32:08,739 --> 00:32:10,339
He won't suffer anymore.

575
00:32:11,020 --> 00:32:13,219
Now he's with your parents.

576
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:17,900
But I'm still not happy at all.

577
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:21,180
Granny Chen told me that

578
00:32:22,099 --> 00:32:25,619
my brother won't suffer in a family like ours.

579
00:32:26,979 --> 00:32:28,219
But...

580
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:31,420
But I'm still sad.

581
00:32:32,420 --> 00:32:33,859
Sister A' Li.

582
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:40,259
What sins have we done?

583
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:43,619
Why does God just refuse to treat us well?

584
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:48,458
You has done nothing wrong.

585
00:32:48,459 --> 00:32:50,140
It's the fault of endless war.

586
00:32:50,699 --> 00:32:53,020
I was born in a wealthy family.

587
00:32:53,619 --> 00:32:55,539
We swam in luxury.

588
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:57,300
We went out by beautiful carriage.

589
00:32:58,459 --> 00:33:00,020
We lived in a fantastic mansion.

590
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:05,579
But everyone wanted more.

591
00:33:07,979 --> 00:33:10,780
I have thought that if I were born into a peasant family,

592
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:13,900
I would have been able to live in peace.

593
00:33:15,619 --> 00:33:16,979
But I'm wrong.

594
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:19,830
I should understand earlier that

595
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:22,319
in troubled times,

596
00:33:23,079 --> 00:33:25,280
if death can make my wish realized,

597
00:33:26,039 --> 00:33:27,959
that will be much easier.

598
00:33:29,039 --> 00:33:30,839
Here you are.

599
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:33,400
Have a taste.

600
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:36,760
Let's go.

601
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,399
A' Li.

602
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:50,480
Did Ms. Wu take you to see anything?

603
00:33:51,039 --> 00:33:52,438
Taoist.

604
00:33:52,439 --> 00:33:55,600
Could you teach me how to save these refugees?

605
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:59,350
Why do you have that thought?

606
00:33:59,989 --> 00:34:01,550
I hope we can lead a peaceful life.

607
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:03,830
I go with the flow, like duckweed.

608
00:34:04,389 --> 00:34:07,429
You can see heaven and earth, and all living creatures in the world.

609
00:34:07,430 --> 00:34:09,869
It seems that your heart has been cured.

610
00:34:13,050 --> 00:34:15,550
<i>[Dapu Inn]</i>

611
00:34:17,949 --> 00:34:19,630
We're in Luoyang now.

612
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:23,389
Let's settle down here.

613
00:34:23,390 --> 00:34:24,190
Mr. Qin.

614
00:34:24,749 --> 00:34:26,349
Is Changge really in Luoyang?

615
00:34:26,350 --> 00:34:29,188
If you don't believe my intelligence, you'd better find her alone.

616
00:34:29,189 --> 00:34:30,310
Xu Feng.

617
00:34:36,269 --> 00:34:37,188
Grandpa Qin.

618
00:34:37,189 --> 00:34:38,870
What's wrong with Brother Azhun?

619
00:34:40,269 --> 00:34:42,309
Nothing wrong with him.

620
00:34:42,310 --> 00:34:44,590
He's afraid he won't find your Brother Li.

621
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:56,630
Thank you for your kindness.

622
00:35:19,189 --> 00:35:20,149
Sister A' Li.

623
00:35:20,150 --> 00:35:21,549
You're quite a fast learner.

624
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:23,350
You are more skillful in pounding herbs.

625
00:35:26,029 --> 00:35:27,829
Come here, everyone!

626
00:35:27,830 --> 00:35:30,070
