627
00:35:30,670 --> 00:35:31,910
Princess.

628
00:35:34,709 --> 00:35:35,910
Princess!

629
00:35:42,350 --> 00:35:43,789
Princess!

630
00:35:47,469 --> 00:35:49,110
Princess, here you come!

631
00:36:18,269 --> 00:36:19,150
Changge.

632
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:22,149
You don't hate me?

633
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:24,070
I was so stubborn that

634
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,429
I always refused you.

635
00:36:27,469 --> 00:36:28,469
Leyan.

636
00:36:29,429 --> 00:36:30,709
Can you forgive me?

637
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:37,269
I've never blamed you.

638
00:36:39,749 --> 00:36:43,070
Thanks to God, we can meet again.

639
00:36:43,949 --> 00:36:48,268
I really thought I'd never see you again.

640
00:36:48,269 --> 00:36:50,830
The fate has brought us together again.

641
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:53,550
Don't cry.

642
00:36:55,870 --> 00:36:56,830
How about you?

643
00:36:57,590 --> 00:36:59,029
Are you Ookay?

644
00:37:00,630 --> 00:37:04,228
Where did you go after we farewell in a hurry in Youzhou?

645
00:37:04,229 --> 00:37:06,029
Did you go directly to Luoyang?

646
00:37:06,789 --> 00:37:10,469
After leaving Youzhou, I went all the way north.

647
00:37:11,229 --> 00:37:13,150
Then I met Taoist Sun.

648
00:37:13,749 --> 00:37:17,590
It's a long story.

649
00:37:20,469 --> 00:37:21,949
You must have suffered a lot.

650
00:37:22,830 --> 00:37:24,670
You went through many difficulties, right?

651
00:37:27,269 --> 00:37:28,189
Let bygones be bygones.

652
00:37:28,910 --> 00:37:30,670
Don't mention it.

653
00:37:31,749 --> 00:37:35,910
By the way, we almost met each other before.

654
00:37:36,469 --> 00:37:37,590
What do you mean?

655
00:37:38,390 --> 00:37:40,228
Do you remember the purse I gave you?

656
00:37:40,229 --> 00:37:42,029
I embroiled a new one which is exactly alike.

657
00:37:42,910 --> 00:37:44,310
I remember that.

658
00:37:44,910 --> 00:37:47,708
I was confused that why someone knew

659
00:37:47,709 --> 00:37:49,749
what the purse you gave me was like.

660
00:37:50,269 --> 00:37:51,988
Why didn't you see me?

661
00:37:51,989 --> 00:37:53,469
I went to see you.

662
00:37:54,110 --> 00:37:56,468
But Hao Du arrived in advance.

663
00:37:56,469 --> 00:38:01,709
Although Hao Du is not a good man, he can protect you.

664
00:38:02,749 --> 00:38:06,269
By the way, why were you in Yunzhou then?

665
00:38:18,830 --> 00:38:20,070
Commandant.

666
00:38:26,310 --> 00:38:27,349
Where's Princess?

667
00:38:27,350 --> 00:38:28,350
Her Highness is ahead.

668
00:38:31,390 --> 00:38:32,508
Princess.

669
00:38:32,509 --> 00:38:33,508
Princess!

670
00:38:33,509 --> 00:38:34,428
Princess!

671
00:38:34,429 --> 00:38:35,590
Mr. Hao is here.

672
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:37,670
Hao Du?

673
00:38:38,469 --> 00:38:39,550
Changge.

674
00:38:40,429 --> 00:38:41,629
Changge.

675
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:43,589
I have a lot to tell you.

676
00:38:43,590 --> 00:38:45,069
Wait for me in the market between 3 to 5 pm.

677
00:38:45,070 --> 00:38:46,149
Go. Hurry up.

678
00:38:46,150 --> 00:38:47,028
Be careful.

679
00:38:47,029 --> 00:38:47,949
Hurry up!

680
00:38:56,310 --> 00:38:57,110
Hao Du!

681
00:38:59,670 --> 00:39:00,708
I've finished my business.

682
00:39:00,709 --> 00:39:01,188
Let's go back.

683
00:39:01,189 --> 00:39:01,989
Wait a minute.

684
00:39:04,949 --> 00:39:06,070
What's wrong, Princess?

685
00:39:07,709 --> 00:39:08,869
I have a stomachache.

686
00:39:08,870 --> 00:39:09,909
We have doctors here.

687
00:39:09,910 --> 00:39:10,589
Doctor!

688
00:39:10,590 --> 00:39:12,229
No need. It's just my period.

689
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:18,870
An Rou.

690
00:39:25,269 --> 00:39:26,309
Let me do that.

691
00:39:26,310 --> 00:39:27,110
Take it.

692
00:39:37,269 --> 00:39:38,428
Hold on.

693
00:39:38,429 --> 00:39:39,709
The carriage is over there.

694
00:39:45,830 --> 00:39:47,110
3 to 5 p.m, market.

695
00:39:53,749 --> 00:39:56,670
<i>What happened to them?</i>

696
00:39:57,310 --> 00:39:59,310
<i>[Spring Breeze and Evening Water]</i>

697
00:40:00,310 --> 00:40:05,549
