714
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:50,269
Do you want to fight against me?

715
00:40:51,390 --> 00:40:52,708
Okay.

716
00:40:52,709 --> 00:40:54,508
I think all of us has put up with you for a long time.

717
00:40:54,509 --> 00:40:58,229
If Mr. Qin didn't stop me, I would have beat you up!

718
00:41:02,509 --> 00:41:03,788
Okay.

719
00:41:03,789 --> 00:41:05,029
Have a try.

720
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:14,748
I'm old.

721
00:41:14,749 --> 00:41:17,948
If the young men want to fight, go outside.

722
00:41:17,949 --> 00:41:19,509
Don't tear down the house.

723
00:41:20,390 --> 00:41:21,269
Go!

724
00:41:22,029 --> 00:41:23,110
