00:43:27,749 --> 00:43:28,508
Bros!

740
00:43:28,509 --> 00:43:29,669
Go on!

741
00:43:29,670 --> 00:43:30,669
He's going to the limit!

742
00:43:30,670 --> 00:43:31,790
I'm willing to admit defeat.

743
00:43:32,350 --> 00:43:33,269
You win!

